{
  "stem": "1550.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So what happened then, we decided to break up the ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ship was, to a certain extent, made out of wood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the decks and the interior partitions, everything was made out of wood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we started to take all the wood-- we ripped up all the decks and took out all of the partitions-- the cabins, all the-- everything made out of wood was ripped up and cut into little pieces.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a long chain of people going into the engine room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all those pieces were sent down into the engine and [INAUDIBLE] thrown into the-- into the boiler-- into the furnace.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in this fashion, we were able to continue for a few more days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- the ship was going a little bit, and then it came to a standstill, because there was not enough steam there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we chopped up more wood, got it back in, and continued again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this went on for a few more days until we eventually saw land in the distance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But just before we did that, during that period-- by the way, our ship did not have a radio.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were-- there were no ways we could-- could communicate with anybody, and there was no way we could get help from anybody.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But during those few days when we were in this-- in this situation, we were caught by two destroyers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two British Destroyers, fortunately.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not Italians but British.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came along, and they came with great speed, and they circled around and they [? semaphored ?] with this thing here and said, who are you?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we said back, we are Jewish refugees and we need help.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they said, I'm sorry, we can't help you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
